    >, even if the author is a student.
  </p>
  <p>
    One "Regular" or "IEEE Members" registration can cover <span
      class="font-bold text-red-500">at most 2</span
    > accepted paper.
  </p>
  <p>
    Each accepted paper is required to be <span class="font-bold text-red-500"
      >fully registered by August 1</span
    >; otherwise, the paper will not be included in the conference proceedings
    and IEEE Xplore.
  </p>
